window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Treasures of Alexander are mythic-grade artifacts.</b></p> <p>They are the greatest weapons of humankind against the demon threat looming over them. The Dukes and Duchesses of the Netherworld won't remain idle. They will do whatever it takes to upheave the Conference of Alyras and steal the Treasures of Alexander.</p> <p>While this is happening, Salvos will have to come to grips with taking care of the newborn Wyverns...</p> <p><i>The Treasures of Alexander </i>is book 8 in the Salvos series.</p>"; 
